                       "message":  "SCENE-OPEN-WIRING: correction - refresh GLB-only Open docs + pin literal .rge-project test\n\nAddresses the post-exec review (NEEDS_CORRECTION).\n\n1. Refresh 5 stale production comments that still described Ctrl+O as GLB-only (the open_dialog field, attach_glb_loader_hook, with_glb_open_dialog, and the window_event Ctrl+O comment in editor-shell; the Open-dialog-hook section banner in the binary) to describe the GLB-or-scene Open surface. The Glb-prefixed API names are kept per the accepted cosmetic-rename deferral.\n\n2. Add scene_open_accepts_literal_rge_project - a headless test pinning the literal extensionless .rge-project handler path (the motivating case for the All-Files dialog resolution): asserts the world swap and glb_source_path clear.\n\nProduction doc comments + one headless test only; no design / API / dependency change. Canonical gate green (VERIFY OK, 7 steps).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e",
